  "texts": [
    "All videos are extracted at 30 FPS, and the main video features are subsampled to 3 FPS after the trimming.",
    "We set F = 100 as the final number of frames for the subglobal feature.",
    "The text decoder is truncated or padded to L v = L p = 1024 tokens.",
    "We apply the Adam optimizer [14] with a learning rate 3 • 10 -4, a cosine learning rate decay and a warm-up period.",
    "All of our models are fine-tuned with batch size 1 for 30 epochs on an NVIDIA RTX-3060 GPU for around 8 hours."
  ],
